text: Kukkuyanovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kukkuyanovsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 708 as of 2010. There are 8 streets. == Geography == It is located 22 km from Dyurtyuli. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Kukkuyanovo
